{"tid":1338535,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"施永青: be water","createTime":"2019-07-21T13:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T11:51:32.000Z","uid":263452,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"38e9fd89660ffb3de18e5b0cba53f6cbc9ce35c3","tid":1338535,"uid":263452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:43:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.centanet.com/home/ColumnArticle.aspx?id=11837\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.centanet.com%2Fhome%2FColumnArticle.aspx%3Fid%3D11837&d=7LXG2TbyL57SoPLQ%2FF4DpeCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=f82d48d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.centanet.com/home/ColumnArticle.aspx?id=11837</a><br />\n<br />\n施永青<br />\n2007年4月19日<br />\n<br />\n我告訴同學：人遇到困難的時候，正常的反應是知難而退。這沒有甚麼不對，只要有其他的途徑一樣可以達至目標，為何不試行其他更易行的途徑？ <br />\n老子說：「上善如水。」他認為水的行徑最善，最符合天道。水只會向低流，在遇到阻礙物時，會轉向，繞過就算；除非完全受阻，那就只好停下來，積聚位能，慢慢待水位升高，直到升越阻礙物，才繼續向低流；久而久之，甚至可把阻礙物沖掉，流得更為順暢。 <br />\n毛澤東在打仗時，就不喜歡挑戰困難。若果敵強我弱，當然走為上著。所以他選擇「敵進我退，敵疲我擾，敵退我追」；並主張「在戰術上要以十對一」，即人多欺負人少，以壓倒性優勢去制服敵人，深明孫子所說：「善戰者，勝於易勝者也。」按孫子的說法：「善戰者，無智名、無勇功」，「不戰而屈人之兵」。即是說：善於打仗的人，沒有智慧的名聲，也沒有勇猛的功勞，他之所以打勝仗，是因為他先積累足夠的力量，讓自己立於不敗之地，早已勝券在握，不用開戰，敵人已要逃跑。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來施永青係07年已經做緊臥底<br />\n仲要一路幫我地研究對家D兵法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511e02b9a16b76dad1b6b45f747d423327318f3c","tid":1338535,"uid":263452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:03:38.000Z","msg":"BTW有人比左個耳機我<br />\n話係613係上水5點時圍肥佬天橋執到<br />\n到依家都未搵到失主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beda7aeaefc8104ec59da8cb925914ac82d8bda0","tid":1338535,"uid":263452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:17:11.000Z","msg":"又有多件失物<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事主話佢今日問人借手套<br />\n借完個失主表示會想拎番<br />\n最後現場太亂搵唔番佢<br />\n失主聯絡下我啊唔該<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c7f072ad69ce3a1fae9386c8f994a3d8e11785","tid":1338535,"uid":263452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}